Incidence and mortality of kidney cancers, and human development index in Asia; 
a matter of concern.

Arabsalmani M(1), Mohammadian-Hafshejani A(2), Ghoncheh M(3), Hadadian F(4), 
Towhidi F(5), Vafaee K(5), Salehiniya H(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Epidemiology and Biostatistics, School of Public Health, 
