(2)Social Determinants in Health Promotion Research Center, Hormozgan University 
of Medical Sciences, Bandar Abbas, Iran.
(3)Department of Epidemiology and Biostatistics, School of public health, 
Hamadan University of Medical Sciences, Hamadan, Iran.
(4)Department of Medical Surgical Nursing, School of Nursing and Midwifery, 
Kermanshah University of Medical Sciences, Kermanshah, Iran.
(5)Imam Reza Hospital, Kermanshah University of Medical Sciences, Kermanshah, 
Iran.
(6)Zabol University of Medical Sciences, Zabol, Iran ; Department of 
