between ASIR and ASMR with HDI and its components.
RESULTS: A total of 121 099 kidney cancer cases were recorded in Asian countries 
in 2012.Overall, 80 080 cases (66.12%) were males. Sex ratio was 1.95. The three 
countries with the highest number of new patients were china (66 466 cases), 
Japan (16 830 cases), India(9658 cases), respectively. Positive correlation were 
seen between HDI and ASIR of kidney cancer 0.655 (P = 0.001), and HDI and ASMR 
of kidney cancer 0.285 (P = 0.055).
CONCLUSIONS: A positive relationship between ASIR and the HDI was seen. The 
relationship is due to risk factors in countries with high development such as 
older age, smoking, hypertension, obesity, and diet. However, ASMR showed no 
significant relationship with HDI.

